SELECT r.property_name, COUNT(rp.payment_id) AS total_payments FROM rental_properties r LEFT JOIN leases l ON r.property_id = l.property_id LEFT JOIN rental_payments rp ON l.lease_id = rp.lease_id GROUP BY r.property_id HAVING total_payments > 5 ORDER BY total_payments DESC;
